Package: icedove-3.0
Architecture: any
Depends: fontconfig, psmisc, debianutils (>= 1.16), ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: myspell-en-us | hunspell-dictionary | myspell-dictionary
Suggests: icedove-3.0-gnome-support (= ${binary:Version}), latex-xft-fonts, libthai0
Provides: mail-reader
Section: mail
Description: mail/news client with RSS and integrated spam filter support
 Icedove 3.0 is a mail/news/RSS client.

Package: icedove-3.0-gnome-support
Architecture: any
Section: mail
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, icedove-3.0 (= ${binary:Version})
Provides: gnome-www-browser
Description: Support for Gnome in Icedove 3.0
 This is an extension to Icedove that allows it to use protocol
 handlers from GnomeVFS, such as smb or sftp, and other GNOME
 integration features.

Package: icedove-3.0-dev
Architecture: any
Section: mail
Depends: icedove-3.0 (= ${binary:Version}), icedove-3.0-gnome-support (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development files for Icedove 3.0
 This package contains the development headers, idl files and static libraries 
 needed to develop applications using Icedove.

Package: icedove-3.0-dbg
Architecture: any
Section: mail
